5812 - Eating Places Summary > BEST OCIANA SEAFOOD PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover eating places. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. BEST OCIANA SEAFOOD PTY LTD is headquartered in Mount Gambier, South Australia. It is headed by director & company secretary Martin Hercules Von Stanke. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $35.35 million. Its net loss totalled $1.10 million. BEST OCIANA SEAFOOD PTY LTD forms part of the retail trade industry sector.
